                    PHP 7.3 Lightweight Docker Container                     

  Web Server:     Caddy (port 80)                                            
  PHP:            PHP 7.3-FPM with FastCGI                                  
  Document Root:  /var/www/public                                            
  SSH Access:     root@localhost:22 (password: 1234)                        
  Logs:           docker logs <container-name>                              

  Quick Commands:                                                            
    • supervisorctl status     - Check service status                       
    • docker logs <container>  - View all logs                             
    • php-fpm7.3 -v            - Check PHP version                          
    • caddy version            - Check Caddy version                        
    • composer --version       - Check Composer version                     
    • bun --version            - Check Bun version                          
    • php-dev                  - Enable development mode (Xdebug)           
    • php-prod                 - Enable production mode                     

  Services:       Caddy, PHP-FPM, SSH                                       
  Tools:          Composer, Bun                                              
  Extensions:     MySQL, GD, ZIP, cURL, XML, BCMath, JSON, Intl, Gettext,   
                  Bzip2, Exif, Xdebug                                        

  Base Image:     Debian Bullseye Slim                                      
  PHP Version:    7.3 (Ondřej Surý PPA)                                     
